                     <interp inst="t18470816-1846-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp> for feloniously and knowingly uttering a forged request for the delivery of 2 1/4 yards of kerseymere, with intent to defraud <persName id="t18470816-name-691" type="victimName">
